room_title: Escape room "Kraken Kwest" by Epoch Escapes in Jefferson City
room_address: 3600 Country Club Dr #318 Jefferson City, MO 65109
room_description: Piracy doesn’t offer much in the way of retirement, but one could hope for a career end better than this… You and your crew have sailed to every corner of the seven seas, and in your tireless search for riches you discovered a place called Treasure Island. It was there you unlocked the wrong box, and you have been cursed with the Mark of the Kraken. For months you have searched for the Legendary Papers of Whypos while being trailed closely by the supernatural beast… your search has led you what seems to be an abandoned fortress of sorts. The Kraken is closing in. Find the Legendary Papers of Whypos and cleanse yourselves of Mark before time runs out!
